title: Backgammon Classic 6.2.zip
description:
Backgammon Classic - 6.2

This version has a new design, more strength, many playing options and an intuitive interface! Three different levels, from beginner to advanced, can extend your fun and improve your skills! Selectable skin, game or match play, statistical information, save/load a game, doubling cube, several playing levels and player ratings are a few of our backgammon features.


Works with XP/Vista
